description:
This is a 45 minute workout called '45 Minute Indoor Cycling Ramp Workout | From Threshold To Sprints!' from the channel GCN Training.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Advanced and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.
